data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Adjacent to Lake Jane Estates Park w/Baseball Field, Tennis Courts, Covered Picnic Area & Private Community Pool. Across the street, you'll love the private dock w/access for fishing on Lake Debra Jane! Close to Lake Tapps & all it has to offer! 5 Bed, 3 Bath Daylight Rambler w/Den! There's room for it all in this updated home w/Newer Stainless Steel Appliances and new Laminate Floors, Paint and White Doors & Millwork. Open Concept Main Floor Kitchen, Living & Dining. Family Rm, Den, 4th & 5th Beds & 3rd Bath Down. Primary Bed w/En Suite Bath & Walk-In Closet. 2 Fireplaces to keep you comfortable all year long! Massive .34 Lot w/Covered Patio & Outdoor Kitchen. 2-Car Garage + RV/Boat Parking.
